*Leto* je bilo veoma toplo. (The summer was very warm.)

*Letu* smo proveli u prirodi. (We spent the summer in nature.)

Ovo *leto* je bilo posebno zanimljivo. (This summer was particularly interesting.)

On je prošlo *leto* proveo u inostranstvu. (He spent last summer abroad.)

Najlepše *leto* sam provela sa svojom porodicom. (I spent the most beautiful summer with my family.)